(Hindi lang basta tahanan ang pinoprotektahan ko.)

00:41:07.355 --> 00:41:09.400
(Hindi lang pagiging anak ang ginagawa ko,)

00:41:10.550 --> 00:41:11.510
(hindi lang basta asawa,)

